1
00:00:06,356 --> 00:00:06,752
Fine.

2
00:00:06,752 --> 00:00:08,355
I'll have them make you something.

3
00:00:08,355 --> 00:00:09,156
It won't take long.

4
00:00:09,716 --> 00:00:10,196
No need.

5
00:00:10,196 --> 00:00:10,835
It's fine.

6
00:00:12,076 --> 00:00:13,196
Your noodles are the best.

7
00:00:15,996 --> 00:00:16,996
The sweet talker.

8
00:00:20,876 --> 00:00:21,355
Yunian.

9
00:00:22,195 --> 00:00:23,075
Here, put this on.

10
00:00:23,756 --> 00:00:25,156
You should head back.

11
00:00:25,156 --> 00:00:26,235
I can manage myself.

12
00:00:26,752 --> 00:00:27,636
Absolutely not.

13
00:00:27,636 --> 00:00:28,276
It's so late.

14
00:00:28,276 --> 00:00:29,316
You're a young woman.

15
00:00:29,316 --> 00:00:30,276
I'm taking you home.

16
00:00:30,276 --> 00:00:31,515
Tell me where you live.

17
00:00:31,956 --> 00:00:32,395
It's okay.

18
00:00:32,395 --> 00:00:34,395
I'll call a ride later.

19
00:00:35,555 --> 00:00:37,156
You've got lots of guests waiting.

20
00:00:37,156 --> 00:00:38,075
Go on back.

21
00:00:38,848 --> 00:00:39,795
Tell you what, Yunian.

22
00:00:40,435 --> 00:00:41,395
I'll arrange a car.

23
00:00:41,475 --> 00:00:42,715
Tell the driver your address

24
00:00:43,516 --> 00:00:44,236
to take you home.

25
00:00:44,236 --> 00:00:45,316
- Alright?
- No need.

26
00:00:47,196 --> 00:00:48,276
Let's go, Yunian.

27
00:00:48,276 --> 00:00:49,075
You've had too much.

28
00:00:49,155 --> 00:00:49,916
Come with me.

29
00:00:51,035 --> 00:00:52,556
Thank you.

30
00:00:53,556 --> 00:00:54,916
You made me believe

31
00:00:55,155 --> 00:00:56,236
that a place like this

32
00:00:56,236 --> 00:00:57,395
still have genuine feelings.

33
00:00:57,916 --> 00:00:59,596
You gave me the confidence to stay.

34
00:01:03,276 --> 00:01:04,355
Thank you, Ruxue.

35
00:01:05,435 --> 00:01:06,236
Thank you.

36
00:01:14,676 --> 00:01:15,515
Take it easy.

37
00:01:24,235 --> 00:01:25,155
Haven't you noticed

38
00:01:26,155 --> 00:01:27,595
that Feng and Jiasheng

39
00:01:28,036 --> 00:01:29,276
seem a bit off lately?

40
00:01:31,515 --> 00:01:32,996
It'd be weird if they get along.

41
00:01:33,476 --> 00:01:34,276
Feng's autocratic.

42
00:01:34,276 --> 00:01:35,155
Jiasheng's tough.

43
00:01:35,556 --> 00:01:36,715
Have they ever got along?

44
00:01:39,435 --> 00:01:40,836
You men are so oblivious.

45
00:01:42,836 --> 00:01:43,795
Don't you think

46
00:01:43,996 --> 00:01:45,996
they talk less and less these days?

47
00:01:46,515 --> 00:01:47,595
Other than when

48
00:01:47,836 --> 00:01:49,235
you three reconcile

49
00:01:49,235 --> 00:01:50,036
monthly,

50
00:01:50,476 --> 00:01:51,996
do they ever talk privately?

51
00:01:52,435 --> 00:01:53,036
We're guys.

52
00:01:53,196 --> 00:01:54,875
Why would we chat for no reason?

53
00:01:56,396 --> 00:01:57,036
No.

54
00:01:58,315 --> 00:01:59,996
Ever since An Ruoxi's death,

55
00:02:00,715 --> 00:02:02,155
they've been off.

56
00:02:04,836 --> 00:02:06,276
After Ruoxi's death,

57
00:02:07,036 --> 00:02:08,276
Jiasheng has changed.

58
00:02:09,515 --> 00:02:10,715
Su Yunian

59
00:02:11,116 --> 00:02:12,355
looks so much like An Ruoxi.

60
00:02:12,875 --> 00:02:14,715
Why's Jiasheng so hung up on one woman?

61
00:02:16,595 --> 00:02:17,396
Not like you,

62
00:02:18,076 --> 00:02:19,396
through all the beauties,

63
00:02:19,396 --> 00:02:20,396
not a trace left on you.

64
00:02:24,796 --> 00:02:26,315
That's only because a certain someone

65
00:02:26,915 --> 00:02:27,996
isn't in that garden.

66
00:02:29,796 --> 00:02:31,236
If she were there,

67
00:02:32,796 --> 00:02:33,635
I'd never leave her.

68
00:02:35,715 --> 00:02:36,915
Easy, Yunian.

69
00:02:36,915 --> 00:02:37,356
Slow down.

70
00:02:37,836 --> 00:02:38,676
Steps ahead.

71
00:02:38,676 --> 00:02:39,155
Steps!

72
00:02:39,155 --> 00:02:40,035
Watch your step!

73
00:02:40,475 --> 00:02:41,076
Steady!

74
00:02:44,076 --> 00:02:44,875
Slow down!

75
00:02:44,956 --> 00:02:45,635
The car's here.

76
00:02:45,635 --> 00:02:46,116
Up front.

77
00:02:49,024 --> 00:02:49,796
Come on.

78
00:02:56,035 --> 00:02:56,595
Let's go.

79
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,035
Stop the car!

80
00:02:58,755 --> 00:02:59,475
Stop!

81
00:03:00,035 --> 00:03:00,875
Stop!

82
00:03:03,155 --> 00:03:04,356
Ruxue, whose car is that?

83
00:03:04,715 --> 00:03:06,155
Chu Bai, why are you running out?

84
00:03:09,035 --> 00:03:10,676
Where are you taking Su Yunian?

85
00:03:10,676 --> 00:03:11,516
She's drunk.

86
00:03:11,516 --> 00:03:12,796
I'm getting her a ride home.

87
00:03:12,796 --> 00:03:13,755
Don't worry.

88
00:03:14,195 --> 00:03:15,475
Get back to work.

89
00:03:34,276 --> 00:03:35,396
Thank you, Lu.

90
00:03:40,516 --> 00:03:41,915
What are you thanking me for?

91
00:03:47,595 --> 00:03:48,435
I know.

92
00:03:49,116 --> 00:03:50,635
If you hadn't

93
00:03:50,796 --> 00:03:51,836
protected me,

94
00:03:53,076 --> 00:03:53,875
I might have

95
00:03:54,396 --> 00:03:57,076
made the same mistake as Yunyan did.

96
00:03:57,996 --> 00:03:59,076
Don't even know

97
00:03:59,076 --> 00:04:00,155
if I'd still be alive.

98
00:04:21,715 --> 00:04:22,796
Haiwei East Road.

99
00:04:22,796 --> 00:04:23,635
Thanks.

100
00:04:24,916 --> 00:04:25,875
Don't worry.

101
00:04:25,875 --> 00:04:27,395
I'll get you there.

102
00:04:31,635 --> 00:04:32,676
Mr. Lin,

103
00:04:33,955 --> 00:04:35,236
why is it you?

104
00:04:36,672 --> 00:04:39,840
=The Glory Fades=

105
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,560
=Episode 14=
(A Sheep in Tiger's Den)

106
00:04:43,036 --> 00:04:44,556
I thought

107
00:04:45,435 --> 00:04:47,395
maybe I was not good enough.

108
00:04:48,395 --> 00:04:50,356
Compared to the girls we selected,

109
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,955
I just had an ordinary

110
00:04:53,075 --> 00:04:54,676
undergraduate degree.

111
00:04:55,036 --> 00:04:55,955
So then I

112
00:04:55,955 --> 00:04:57,395
studied hard,

113
00:04:57,996 --> 00:05:00,036
took advanced courses,
and prepared for grad school.

114
00:05:01,835 --> 00:05:02,596
Later I felt

115
00:05:02,596 --> 00:05:04,356
maybe I was not pretty enough.

116
00:05:05,476 --> 00:05:07,036
Compared to our girls,

117
00:05:07,036 --> 00:05:08,195
I'm just average.

118
00:05:08,676 --> 00:05:09,596
So then I

119
00:05:09,596 --> 00:05:10,596
spent money

120
00:05:11,476 --> 00:05:12,916
on treatments and upkeep,

121
00:05:12,955 --> 00:05:14,556
learned dance and practiced yoga.

122
00:05:15,435 --> 00:05:16,515
Later I felt

123
00:05:17,195 --> 00:05:18,315
I didn't understand him.

124
00:05:19,236 --> 00:05:20,635
Like that kind

125
00:05:21,195 --> 00:05:22,835
of care and love for him

126
00:05:23,716 --> 00:05:25,435
couldn't reach his heart.

127
00:05:26,596 --> 00:05:27,835
So I would

128
00:05:28,515 --> 00:05:29,476
find ways

129
00:05:29,476 --> 00:05:30,955
to try to

130
00:05:31,116 --> 00:05:32,315
understand him better.

131
00:05:34,435 --> 00:05:35,236
But it didn't work.

132
00:05:35,556 --> 00:05:36,635
No.

133
00:05:37,955 --> 00:05:39,515
Wrong is just wrong.

134
00:05:42,275 --> 00:05:43,875
An Ruoxi was the right one.

135
00:05:46,236 --> 00:05:48,075
You really dosed her heavily.

136
00:05:48,075 --> 00:05:49,476
From Deep In The Bustle

137
00:05:49,476 --> 00:05:50,435
to the hotel shortly,

138
00:05:50,716 --> 00:05:51,716
Su Yunian

139
00:05:51,916 --> 00:05:53,315
hasn't regained consciousness yet.

140
00:05:53,635 --> 00:05:54,435
Don't worry.

141
00:05:55,236 --> 00:05:56,195
This girl

142
00:05:56,195 --> 00:05:57,835
will be handled perfectly.

143
00:06:06,912 --> 00:06:08,768
(Chu Bai)

144
00:06:09,755 --> 00:06:10,635
The right person

145
00:06:12,236 --> 00:06:13,796
can do no wrong.

146
00:06:17,116 --> 00:06:18,116
That's why the noodles

147
00:06:19,476 --> 00:06:21,435
you make are the best.

148
00:06:28,476 --> 00:06:29,356
Lu,

149
00:06:31,755 --> 00:06:33,515
I understand your feelings,

150
00:06:35,556 --> 00:06:37,275
but we're not from the same world.

151
00:06:43,835 --> 00:06:44,635
Tell me.

152
00:06:46,515 --> 00:06:49,156
Since Su Yunian looks
so much like An Ruoxi,

153
00:06:50,435 --> 00:06:51,875
why did Jiasheng drive her away?

154
00:06:53,075 --> 00:06:54,435
Couldn't they just be together?

155
00:06:57,635 --> 00:06:59,116
Perhaps for Jiasheng,

156
00:07:00,315 --> 00:07:01,916
there's only one An Ruoxi.

157
00:07:07,075 --> 00:07:08,195
True.

158
00:07:09,596 --> 00:07:10,955
There's only one An Ruoxi.

159
00:07:12,556 --> 00:07:13,755
No one can replace her.

160
00:07:20,036 --> 00:07:20,676
Come in.

161
00:07:20,832 --> 00:07:25,600
(LXR Hotel, Changqingtai City)

162
00:07:29,835 --> 00:07:31,116
Sleep with you and get paid?

163
00:07:31,116 --> 00:07:32,556
Is there such a good deal?

164
00:07:32,955 --> 00:07:34,835
It'll be a fun night.

165
00:08:36,416 --> 00:08:39,136
(Three days later)

166
00:08:42,112 --> 00:08:43,744
(Deep In The Bustle)

167
00:08:44,256 --> 00:08:45,952
(Dragon Soars, Phoenix Sings
Beauty Contest)

168
00:08:47,956 --> 00:08:50,035
Ms. Bai, I didn't expect

169
00:08:50,035 --> 00:08:51,236
Lin Shen would seize...

170
00:08:51,236 --> 00:08:52,035
Bai Ruxue!

171
00:08:53,635 --> 00:08:54,555
A sheep in tiger's den.

172
00:08:54,996 --> 00:08:56,476
Don't you understand that?

173
00:08:58,755 --> 00:09:00,436
Considering you once helped me,

174
00:09:01,356 --> 00:09:02,635
I'll remind you one more time.

175
00:09:03,596 --> 00:09:04,675
At Deep In The Bustle,

176
00:09:04,875 --> 00:09:06,035
Jiasheng is in charge.

177
00:09:06,515 --> 00:09:07,596
Remember that.

178
00:09:08,795 --> 00:09:09,956
I know I was wrong.

179
00:09:10,755 --> 00:09:12,076
I'll apologize to her now.

180
00:09:12,515 --> 00:09:13,555
Something like this

181
00:09:13,555 --> 00:09:15,076
can't be fixed with an apology.

182
00:09:17,836 --> 00:09:18,675
Where's Su Yunian?

183
00:09:18,836 --> 00:09:19,395
Su Yu...

184
00:09:19,596 --> 00:09:20,116
She

185
00:09:20,116 --> 00:09:21,236
is getting makeup done.

186
00:09:21,236 --> 00:09:22,436
Should be ready soon.

187
00:09:32,316 --> 00:09:34,436
You still look a bit pale today.

188
00:09:36,956 --> 00:09:37,635
I'm fine.

189
00:09:37,956 --> 00:09:39,236
Thanks for your concern.

190
00:09:41,795 --> 00:09:43,196
Not good to be a server?

191
00:09:43,436 --> 00:09:45,436
Why insist on joining
the Beauty Contest?

192
00:09:47,236 --> 00:09:48,275
Since I'm here,

193
00:09:48,716 --> 00:09:50,316
I have to climb step by step.

194
00:09:52,596 --> 00:09:53,635
This path

195
00:09:53,996 --> 00:09:54,875
isn't easy.

196
00:09:56,476 --> 00:09:58,515
If you can't climb up
or accidentally fall,

197
00:09:58,996 --> 00:09:59,956
it'll hurt a lot.

198
00:10:05,635 --> 00:10:06,436
Just tell me.

199
00:10:09,836 --> 00:10:11,795
Make me look as much like An Ruoxi
as possible.

200
00:10:12,836 --> 00:10:13,515
Okay?

201
00:10:16,555 --> 00:10:18,395
There's only one An Ruoxi.

202
00:10:18,915 --> 00:10:20,515
Even if her own sister

203
00:10:21,996 --> 00:10:23,476
couldn't take her place.

204
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:26,515
By the way,

205
00:10:27,076 --> 00:10:28,675
can you make friendship bracelets?

206
00:10:30,716 --> 00:10:32,915
I have a really nice bracelet cord.

207
00:10:33,076 --> 00:10:33,675
It's broken.

208
00:10:35,116 --> 00:10:36,356
Can you show it to me?

209
00:10:36,596 --> 00:10:37,915
I might be able to fix it.

210
00:10:41,155 --> 00:10:41,956
Find it yourself.

211
00:10:54,356 --> 00:10:56,635
You and Meng Yin became good friends,

212
00:10:56,635 --> 00:10:58,236
because you're both incredibly genuine.

213
00:10:58,436 --> 00:10:59,755
People in our family

214
00:10:59,996 --> 00:11:01,596
are sincere right down to the bone.

215
00:11:01,996 --> 00:11:02,795
Just look at you.

216
00:11:03,116 --> 00:11:04,915
Being at Deep In The Bustle for so long,

217
00:11:05,035 --> 00:11:05,956
you haven't changed.

218
00:11:11,035 --> 00:11:12,836
Look at these stones we just picked up.

219
00:11:13,755 --> 00:11:15,436
They lay at the bottom of the sea long,

220
00:11:16,316 --> 00:11:17,476
washed ashore,

221
00:11:18,436 --> 00:11:19,596
and now under the sunlight,

222
00:11:19,915 --> 00:11:21,996
they shine even brighter
and more translucent.

223
00:11:23,035 --> 00:11:24,436
I want to be like these stones.

224
00:11:24,836 --> 00:11:26,196
The deeper in the dye vat,

225
00:11:26,316 --> 00:11:27,395
the clearer I must be.

226
00:11:29,356 --> 00:11:30,275
Drill a hole in them,

227
00:11:30,436 --> 00:11:31,476
and they could probably

228
00:11:31,476 --> 00:11:32,795
be strung into a lovely bracelet.

229
00:11:33,275 --> 00:11:34,875
I'll braid you a decorative cord for it.

230
00:11:35,035 --> 00:11:35,596
Ruoxi,

231
00:11:35,716 --> 00:11:37,836
trust my craftsmanship and taste.

232
00:11:38,236 --> 00:11:39,076
I do.

233
00:11:39,196 --> 00:11:40,316
I absolutely do.

234
00:11:40,956 --> 00:11:42,515
Once done, I'll give it to Meng Yin.

235
00:11:42,555 --> 00:11:43,675
She'll love it.

236
00:11:44,915 --> 00:11:46,395
Just a few stones?

237
00:11:46,915 --> 00:11:48,356
Isn't that a bit half-hearted?

238
00:11:49,035 --> 00:11:50,395
It's the thought that counts.

239
00:11:51,116 --> 00:11:51,956
She understands me.

240
00:11:52,956 --> 00:11:53,996
Help me pick one.

241
00:11:53,996 --> 00:11:55,035
Which one looks best?

242
00:11:57,555 --> 00:11:58,875
Well then,

243
00:11:59,875 --> 00:12:00,596
this one.

244
00:12:08,795 --> 00:12:10,155
Let me tell you something.

245
00:12:10,795 --> 00:12:11,555
You

246
00:12:11,555 --> 00:12:13,635
are Ms. Bai's top recommendation.

247
00:12:13,915 --> 00:12:14,795
Later,

248
00:12:14,795 --> 00:12:15,635
go with whoever

249
00:12:15,635 --> 00:12:16,596
takes charge of you.

250
00:12:16,716 --> 00:12:17,755
Do not wander off.

251
00:12:18,196 --> 00:12:18,996
Do you understand?

252
00:12:20,275 --> 00:12:20,956
Exactly!

253
00:12:21,116 --> 00:12:24,395
Especially Room 999 on the top floor.

254
00:12:24,395 --> 00:12:25,755
You should never enter it.

255
00:12:26,275 --> 00:12:27,275
Did you hear?

256
00:12:27,275 --> 00:12:28,236
That girl days ago...

257
00:12:28,236 --> 00:12:28,915
Yanzi,

258
00:12:29,035 --> 00:12:30,316
wash my makeup sponge.

259
00:12:34,155 --> 00:12:35,035
Can't hold her tongue,

260
00:12:35,035 --> 00:12:36,196
so I sent her out to reflect.

261
00:12:36,716 --> 00:12:38,368
(Meng Yin was Ruoxi's best friend)

262
00:12:38,368 --> 00:12:39,395
(at Deep In The Bustle.)

263
00:12:39,596 --> 00:12:40,476
(She always said)

264
00:12:40,956 --> 00:12:42,996
(they were more like
each other's shadow.)

265
00:12:43,275 --> 00:12:44,635
(They rarely needed many words)

266
00:12:44,635 --> 00:12:45,996
(to share a silent understanding.)

267
00:12:45,996 --> 00:12:46,915
(Look at it now.)

268
00:12:47,116 --> 00:12:48,116
(Meng Yin)

269
00:12:48,476 --> 00:12:50,144
(is incredibly cautious)

270
00:12:50,144 --> 00:12:51,236
(and treads carefully.)

271
00:12:51,236 --> 00:12:53,356
(If I confess my relationship
with An Ruoxi,)

272
00:12:53,555 --> 00:12:54,956
(will she help me?)

273
00:12:56,436 --> 00:12:57,196
Ms. Bai.

274
00:12:58,716 --> 00:12:59,316
That's enough.

275
00:12:59,316 --> 00:12:59,996
Almost there.

276
00:13:00,996 --> 00:13:01,716
Not bad.

277
00:13:02,116 --> 00:13:03,196
You look more like her now.

278
00:13:04,875 --> 00:13:05,675
Go downstairs.

279
00:13:06,116 --> 00:13:06,915
Alright, let's go.

280
00:13:06,915 --> 00:13:07,675
Follow me.

281
00:13:08,155 --> 00:13:09,076
I'll take you down.

282
00:13:22,555 --> 00:13:25,555
The Beauty Contest
officially begins now.

283
00:13:25,555 --> 00:13:27,035
Let's welcome all the beauties

284
00:13:27,035 --> 00:13:28,956
to make their dazzling entrance.

285
00:13:30,996 --> 00:13:32,275
Dear guests,

286
00:13:32,275 --> 00:13:34,755
tonight's moon glows softly
for our beauties,

287
00:13:34,836 --> 00:13:36,996
and the stage shines bright
with their elegance.

288
00:13:37,196 --> 00:13:38,515
After rounds of competition,

289
00:13:38,515 --> 00:13:41,116
we finally arrive
at the most anticipated moment.

290
00:13:41,395 --> 00:13:43,395
The final group, six peerless stunners,

291
00:13:43,395 --> 00:13:44,875
are taking the stage for the finale.

292
00:13:45,116 --> 00:13:45,716
Chosen from...

293
00:13:45,716 --> 00:13:46,316
Mr. Tu,

294
00:13:46,515 --> 00:13:47,395
Mr. Zhao,

295
00:13:48,116 --> 00:13:50,635
I carry little weight
and my words are insignificant.

296
00:13:50,635 --> 00:13:52,555
Being stood up
is hardly worth mentioning.

297
00:13:52,915 --> 00:13:54,515
But I do not come alone.

298
00:13:54,555 --> 00:13:56,076
I stand here representing

299
00:13:56,076 --> 00:13:58,035
