303
00:14:02,076 --> 00:14:03,236
I know that.

304
00:14:03,236 --> 00:14:05,875
Whether this deal succeeds
or fails is one thing,

305
00:14:06,076 --> 00:14:06,635
but

306
00:14:07,116 --> 00:14:09,476
the very first step between people

307
00:14:09,996 --> 00:14:11,116
should be

308
00:14:11,116 --> 00:14:13,076
sincerity and trust, right?

309
00:14:13,076 --> 00:14:14,555
Yes.

310
00:14:15,436 --> 00:14:16,116
Tang.

311
00:14:16,395 --> 00:14:17,076
Mr. Tang,

312
00:14:17,836 --> 00:14:20,836
