316
00:14:25,956 --> 00:14:26,716
Right, Mr. Tu?

317
00:14:29,116 --> 00:14:29,915
Tang,

318
00:14:30,515 --> 00:14:31,795
in this world,

319
00:14:32,196 --> 00:14:34,236
sometimes we're driven by circumstances.

320
00:14:35,116 --> 00:14:36,476
To be honest with you,

321
00:14:36,555 --> 00:14:38,076
I came back suddenly that day

322
00:14:38,436 --> 00:14:39,596
for the Grand Princess.

323
00:14:40,832 --> 00:14:42,116
I wanted to explain,

324
00:14:42,236 --> 00:14:43,635
but it is classified.

325
00:14:43,875 --> 00:14:44,755
So

326
00:14:45,196 --> 00:14:46,155
please understand.

327
00:14:47,476 --> 00:14:49,275
Since that's the case,

328
00:14:50,675 --> 00:14:51,716
let's not dwell on it.

329
00:14:51,836 --> 00:14:52,875
Let's share this drink.

330
00:15:04,356 --> 00:15:04,956
Tang,

331
00:15:05,476 --> 00:15:06,515
