345
00:15:33,515 --> 00:15:34,116
Impressive.

346
00:15:34,236 --> 00:15:34,996
Truly impressive.

347
00:15:35,236 --> 00:15:35,996
Lu,

348
00:15:36,675 --> 00:15:37,635
