354
00:15:48,116 --> 00:15:50,035
But Miss Su...

355
00:15:51,155 --> 00:15:53,155
I understand this.

356
00:15:53,155 --> 00:15:54,436
Miss Su

357
00:15:54,555 --> 00:15:56,076
