369
00:16:12,915 --> 00:16:13,716
Chat with Mr. Tu.

370
00:16:13,716 --> 00:16:14,316
Alright.

371
00:16:14,436 --> 00:16:14,956
Jiasheng.

372
00:16:14,956 --> 00:16:16,035
