382
00:16:31,555 --> 00:16:32,515
Three fifty.

383
00:16:32,515 --> 00:16:33,555
Four fifty.

384
00:16:33,635 --> 00:16:34,515
One million.

385
00:16:34,836 --> 00:16:35,956
Seems our esteemed guests

386
00:16:35,956 --> 00:16:37,076
all greatly admire

387
00:16:37,076 --> 00:16:38,035
(Display it on the LED screen?)
this young

388
00:16:38,035 --> 00:16:39,316
and beautiful

389
00:16:39,316 --> 00:16:40,356
