411
00:18:19,266 --> 00:18:22,709
♪Even in tears♪

412
00:18:23,458 --> 00:18:27,372
♪It doesn't matter♪

413
00:18:27,554 --> 00:18:31,377
♪We embrace in dreams♪

414
00:18:32,226 --> 00:18:35,664
♪I let down all my defenses♪

415
00:18:36,898 --> 00:18:40,261
♪Though the story has its end♪

416
00:18:41,026 --> 00:18:49,378
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
